            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h1 id=\"day-6-policy-review-graceful-refusal\">Day 6 \u2014 Policy Review &amp; Graceful Refusal</h1>\n<span class=\"paragraph\"><strong>What you will learn</strong>:</span>\n<ul>\n<li>How policy rules are declared as typed <code>PolicyReference</code> objects \u2014 not inline strings</li>\n<li>How <code>detect_prompt_injection()</code> catches override and hearsay-approval patterns</li>\n<li>How <code>evaluate_authority_boundary()</code> scores whether the proposed action is in scope</li>\n<li>Why <strong>three typed outcomes</strong> are safer than a boolean: <code>approved_to_proceed</code> /\n  <code>needs_human_review</code> / <code>not_authorised_to_continue</code></li>\n<li>The adversarial lab: 20 malicious cases across 5 attack buckets</li>\n</ul></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
      "console": []
    },
    {
